1492: Conquest of Paradise;;1992;;PG-13;;Adventure,Biography,Drama;;6.5;;Ridley Scott;;Gérard Depardieu,Armand Assante,Sigourney Weaver,Loren Dean,Ángela Molina,Fernando Rey,Michael Wincott,Tchéky Karyo,Kevin Dunn,Frank Langella,Mark Margolis,Kario Salem,Billy L. Sullivan,John Heffernan,Arnold Vosloo,Steven Waddington,Fernando Guillén Cuervo,José Luis Ferrer;;Big budget account of Christopher Columbus' discovery of the Americas. Released in 1992 to celebrate the 500th anniversary of the discovery. Shows the disastrous effects the Europeans had on the original inhabitants, and Columbus' struggle to civilize the New World.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0103594/